<h2 id="registering-a-service">Registering a Service <a class="headerlink" href="service-shortcuts#registering-a-service" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Next, I want to register this as a service and use it inside of my controller. So hit
<code>shift+command+O</code>, search for <code>services.yml</code>, delete the comments under the
services key, and put our service name there instead. I'll give it a nickname of
<code>quote_generator</code>:</p>
