<p>We've added the argument here, so now we need to go to <code>services.yml</code>, which I'll
move over to. And notice it's highlighting <code>quote_generator</code> with a missing argument
message because it knows that this service has one argument. So we can say <code>@logger</code>,
or even <code>command+O</code> and then use autocomplete to help us:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="2b66876735">
